<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Message Reported</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;">
    <h2>Your Message Has Been Reported</h2>

    <p>Hello {{ reportedUser.firstname }},</p>

    <p>
        One of your messages has been reported by another user.
    </p>

    <h3>Message Content:</h3>
    <blockquote style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 10px; border-left: 4px solid #ccc;">
        {{ messageContent }}
    </blockquote>

    <h3>Reason for the Report:</h3>
    <p><strong>{{ reason }}</strong></p>

    <p>
        The conversation has been temporarily suspended while we review the situation.
    </p>

    <p>
        If you believe this was a mistake, please contact our support team.
    </p>

    <br>

    <p>
        — The Mosaic Team
    </p>
</body>
</html>